Storytelling Principles

1. There is a harmony to the Cosmos, and it is Best to live within it

2. People are born with different gifts, but have a responsibility to use those Gifts to serve God

3. Anyone has a chance to make a difference, and everyone has a contribution to make

4. The divisions between us are, ultimately, illusions

5. We are, all of us, God, with all the attendant privileges and responsibilities.
